<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ ạ̹lhy yạ msyḥy ʿly̱ ạlṣlybi rạ̉ytuka
 hdẖạ dẖnby yạ ḥbyby ʿfwạaⁿ wlysa dẖnbaka
 (fạqbl ḥyạty wạʿtrạfy ạ̉mạma ạlʿạlm bbrika)2
 ạlqrạr - yạ yswʿy yạ yswʿy km̊ ạuḥib̃uka sydy
 (ạuḥib̃uka .. ạ̉sẖkuruka ạ̉nạ ạuqdĩr̊ ṣanyʿuka )2
 2- yạ ạ̹lhy yạ msyḥy ʿly̱ ạlṣlybi rạ̉ytuka
 ʿyãrūka sẖatamūka qạlwạ ạ̉yna ạ̹lhuka
 (qd mnḥ̊tany sẖifạʾaⁿ ạ̉mạm ạlʿạlm bijil̊dika)2
 3- yạ ạ̹lhy yạ msyḥy ʿly̱ ạlṣlybi rạ̉ytuka
 ḍrabūka ṭʿnūka bạlḥrbaẗ fy janbika
 (qd maḥawta ly ậtẖạmy ạ̉mạm ạlʿạlm bṣlbk)2</lyrics>
<title>yạ ạ̹lhy yạ msyḥy</title>
<author>ạlfryq</author>
